      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/72/1403",
      "text": [
        " دَارِ اَلدُّنْيَا أَطْوَلُكُمْ رَاحَةً يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ فِي اَلْمَوْقِفِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1403 - The Messenger of Allah (sw), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said:\n\"The one who prolongs their Qunoot (supplication during prayer) the longest in this worldly life will be granted the longest rest on the Day of Resurrection at the Standing (before Allah (swt))”."
        ]
      }
    },
